     C                     MOVELH4BAN2    D5BAN2           *番地2
     C                     MOVEL'-'       D5BNS2           *番地線2
     C                     MOVELH4BAN3    D5BAN3           *番地3
     C                     MOVEL'-'       D5BNS3           *番地線3
