ER05 INPUT CORRECT FACTORY CODE
ER06 PART MASTER ALREADY DELETED
ER07 PRODUCT QTY SHOULD NOT EXCEED 16 BOXES
ER08 DERIVERY QTY SHOULD NOT EXCEED PRODUCT QTY
ER09 INCORRECT DATE
ER10 NOT EXIST PILOT LOCATION CODE
ER11 NOT EXIST IN PILOT LOCATION CODE MASTER
ER12 LOCATION CODE ALREADY DELETED
ER13 EXIST IN PILOT DATA
ER14 ASSIGN LARGER PILOT LOCATION CODE
ER15 NOT FOUND
ER16 CANNOT ENTER A NAME
ER17 CANNOT BE ASSIGNED LOT NUMBER
ER18 FIRST PAGE
ER19 LAST PAGE
ER20 NOT EXIST IN PART MASTER
ER21 INPUT HN LOCATION
ER22 INPUT CORRECT FACTORY CODE
ER23 LOT NUMBER ALREADY DELETED
ER24 INPUT PROCESS CODE / FACTORY CODE
ER25 INPUT INSP DATA (Y OR N)
ER26 INCORRECT PROCESS CODE
